 narrow therapeutic ranges (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/298446/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Methotrexate, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Siponimod, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, More', 'Megestrol acetate, Estetrol, Ulipristal, Estradiol, Megestrol acetate, Progesterone, Megestrol acetate, Progesterone, Estradiol', 1767369485);
